    <item>
      <title>由于红海危机持续存在，中国增加了波斯湾石油订单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-adds-persian-gulf-oil-bookings-as-red-sea-crisis-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最近几天，中国对从波斯湾运载原油的油轮的预订量有所增加，这进一步表明，在红海航运中断的情况下，最大的进口国正在从该地区采购更多原油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-adds-persian-gulf-oil-bookings-as-red-sea-crisis-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 05:49:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着交易员权衡数据，中国债券热潮降温，前景缓和</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-s-bond-fever-cools-as-traders-weigh-data-easing-prospects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在收益率逼近历史低点后，中国债券的涨势出现疲软迹象，因为人们越来越担心，鉴于货币宽松步伐缓慢和债务供应增加，近期的涨幅可能过度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/china-s-bond-fever-cools-as-traders-weigh-data-easing-prospects</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 05:46:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
